Package com.commander4j.messages

package com.commander4j.messages
The com.commander4j.messages package contains a class for each type of inbound and outbound message.
  • Classes

    Description
    GenericMessageHeader
    All Commander4j xml messages have a standard format.

    IncommingBatchStatusChange class allows an external system to update the APP_MATERIAL_BATCH table.

    IncommingDespatchConfirmation class allows an external system to generate a despatch transaction.
